A [[holarchy|Holarchy]] of [[squads|Autonomous Squad]] and [[chapters|Chapter Meeting]] that generates a distinct product or value stream is called a [[Portfolio]]. XSCALE portfolios are limited in size by the [[Dunbar Number]]. Each portfolio [[continuously adapts|Continuous Adaptation]] its configuration of squads and chapters to its [[release plans|Release Plan]] and business objectives through a [[Portfolio Squad]]. 
